  "detailed_description": "You play as King of Qin, the one ended the 500-year civil war on this land. Act like a King to manage your follower and the royal court and unite the country. Ready to defence your throne?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1348260/extras/949385fc90bf6a56850c819c006b0247.poster.avif?t=1596133708\" width=640 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1348260/extras/949385fc90bf6a56850c819c006b0247.webm?t=1596133708\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1348260/extras/949385fc90bf6a56850c819c006b0247.mp4?t=1596133708\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong><u>Features</u></strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Dynamic Card</strong>: Each follower card is random generate, base on your strategy to pick those followers.<br></li><li><strong>Control Royal Court</strong>: Each royal court card also had its own unique effect, you only can use it when you had well-controlled the royal court.<br></li><li><strong>Events</strong>: Each events card will bring some negative effect, use your follower or royal court member to solve those problems</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1348260/extras/e8445996ad1f59bc892709efa8745165.poster.avif?t=1596133708\" width=640 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1348260/extras/e8445996ad1f59bc892709efa8745165.webm?t=1596133708\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1348260/extras/e8445996ad1f59bc892709efa8745165.mp4?t=1596133708\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong><u>Content</u></strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Story Mode<br></li><li>7 selected country on United Mode</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1348260/extras/ce620d81eff0774387cfe05d4704eb5f.poster.avif?t=1596133708\" width=640 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1348260/extras/ce620d81eff0774387cfe05d4704eb5f.webm?t=1596133708\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1348260/extras/ce620d81eff0774387cfe05d4704eb5f.mp4?t=1596133708\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
